title: Watching wild horses at Arizona’s Salt River (VIDEO)
text:
Watching wild horses at Arizona’s Salt River (VIDEO) Tuesday September 8, 2015 
SALT RIVER, Sept 8 — Floating along with the current, kayakers and paddleboarders on the Salt River in Arizona might catch a glimpse of a special sight: A herd of wild horses out for a swim. — NYT Screen grab of wild horses at the Salt River in Arizona from the NYT video. More Stories for You:
